snippet.title: EVE Online - Reign Quadrant 1 Trailer (2021)
snippet.description:
Achieve tactical supremacy and victory in New Eden with EVE Online's new Quadrant "Reign", the first in 2021!  Start your galactic adventure - play for free at https://bit.ly/play_eve

Launching a new year of Quadrants after 2020's successful introduction of themed content for EVE, Reign brings with it exciting new updates to fleets and travel, continuous balance and meta changes, plus returning events such as the Guardian's Gala and The Hunt.

Music & Sound Design: Makewaves Audio 

Start playing EVE for free at https://bit.ly/play_eve
For past, present and future of EVE Online visit https://bit.ly/updates_eve
